100 Ideas for Teaching Primary Mathematics 
Author(s): Alan Thwaites 
Publisher: Continuum 
Date : 2008 
Pages : 145 
Format : PDF 

This eBook is essential reading for any teacher involved with children's development in the primary school. Focusing on primary mathematics the author provides one hundred practical and inspiring ideas for use in the classroom.
